**Proposal Due Date**
January 2022
**Proposal Overview**
A bridge between BSC and SORA networks.

**Proposal Goals (list with explanations where possible)**
We will have a bridge between SORA and BSC networks. 

**Scope of Work (describe the scope of work in as much detail as possible)**
Build a new bridge the same as between ETH and SORA networks but for BSC and SORA networks.
Integration of new bridge with polkaswap.io

**Current Roadblocks and Barriers to Success**
Bridge between ETH and SORA networks has high ETH fees, and is easy to fail when ETH gas increases.
Many people don't want to use Polkaswap because of ETH fees.
A bridge between BSC and SORA networks can help many people easy to use Polkaswap and SORA Ecosystem.

**Evaluation Metrics and Criteria (definition of done should be as clear as possible)**
Users can transfer assets from BSC network to SORA network and SORA network to BSC network with a new bridge on Polkaswap.io.

**Submission Requirements**
Fulfill evaluation metrics and criteria.
Pull requests to paths as outlined within Submission Method done before Due Date.

**Submission Method (which folder on GitHub to submit a proposal to)** [https://github.com/sora-xor/rfps](https://github.com/sora-xor/rfps)

**Project Due Date**
January 2022
